name: Dread Bread
description: Dread Bread is a hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Vintage Afghani and Colombian Mangobiche. Bred by Bodhi Seeds Dread Bread is 21% THC, making this strain an ideal choice for experienced cannabis consumers. Leafly customers tell us Dread Bread effects make them feel focused, creative, and energetic. Medical marijuana patients often choose Dread Bread when dealing with symptoms associated with stress, depression, and fatigue. The dominant terpene of this cannabis strain is terpinolene. Dread Bread features an aroma and flavor profile of tree fruit, butter, and sage.
